item.description:
above is an image i took at a local lake in 2019, and the cover of my first release under perfectfyfth, init.

whoa.

it’s been over three years since i started releasing music as perfectfyfth, and a lot has changed over that time. i’d like to thank everyone who has been with me since the beginning, as well as everyone who has come along the way, it has been amazing and i have no plans on stopping.

thank you all, take care, and keep your eye out ;)

i was going to write more, but i’m not really sure what to say lol
